<p><em>Disclaimer:</em> Iâ€™m not showing you everything. Again, this isnâ€™t a django tutorial. I expect you to pretty much grasp whatâ€™s going on here without me showing you every import and line of code.</p>

<p>With this, if youâ€™ve set up your project correctly, you can go to your new homepage and see a button. It doesnâ€™t do anything right now. Letâ€™s fix that. First, weâ€™ll set up a new view that just returns a blog post.</p>

