<p>Now if you go to your new blog-post url, you should see the blog post. Nothing new so far. So now, letâ€™s wire this up with htmx. Letâ€™s start by adding the script tag to the home.html template to make sure htmx is available via itâ€™s CDN, and then we can start adding a little htmx magic via directives.</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!-- home.html --&gt;</span>
