<p>So, you can check out the <a href="https://htmx.org/docs/">Htmx documentation</a> to see what Iâ€™ve done here, but the general idea should be obvious; issue a GET request to <code class="highlighter-rouge">/blog-post</code>, then take the response and replace the css selector <code class="highlighter-rouge">#blog-post</code> with the response.</p>

